librtfcomp (1.3-0~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Port to Debian 12 Bookworm.
  * configure.in: Renamed to configure.ac (autoconf modern convention).
  * configure.ac: Replace AM_PROG_LIBTOOL with LT_INIT. Replace pyrexc/PYREX
    with cython3/CYTHON. Set minimum Python version to 3.6 and minimum Cython
    version to 0.29. Rename pyrex_* variables to cython_*. Add brackets to
    AC_COMPILE_IFELSE arguments.
  * acinclude.m4: Replace AC_TRY_CPP with AC_PREPROC_IFELSE. Remove
    AC_REQUIRE([AM_PATH_PYTHON]) (causes m4 divert stack imbalance in modern
    autoconf). Fix print statement to print() call.
  * src/Makefile.am, tests/Makefile.am, python/Makefile.am: Rename deprecated
    INCLUDES to AM_CPPFLAGS.
  * python/Makefile.am: Replace hardcoded pyrexc with $(CYTHON).
  * python/pyrtfcomp.pyx: Add '# cython: language_level=3' directive.
    Replace PyString_AsString/PyString_FromStringAndSize/PyString_AsStringAndSize
    with PyBytes_* equivalents (Python 2 C API removed). Fix print statement
    to print() call.
  * debian/control: Bump debhelper compat to 13, update Standards-Version
    to 4.6.2, change Priority from extra to optional. Update Maintainer.
    Remove XSBC-Original-Maintainer (Ubuntu-specific field). Replace
    python-all-dev + python-pyrex with python3-all-dev + cython3 + dh-python.
    Rename python-rtfcomp to python3-rtfcomp.
  * debian/compat: Removed; debhelper-compat in Build-Depends.
  * debian/rules: Rewrite using dh sequencer with --with python3.
    Add override_dh_makeshlibs to pin shlibs version.
  * debian/*.install: Update library paths to multiarch layout
    (usr/lib/*/lib*).
  * debian/python-rtfcomp.install: Renamed to debian/python3-rtfcomp.install.
  * debian/not-installed: New file; exclude libtool .la file from install.
  * debian/librtfcomp0.lintian-overrides: New file; suppress
    distant-prerequisite-in-shlibs for new package without archive history.

 -- Gustavo Perez Reyes <ghreyes71@gmail.com>  Mon, 02 Mar 2026 22:50:49 -0300

